%h1 Additional Training is Required

%div The training(s) identified below are required to be completed prior to accessing the warehouse.
%div Please contact an administrator to setup your account in the following TalentLMS domain(s) and ensure that the correct email address linked to your warehouse account.
%br
%h2 Account Information
.well
  %div
    Warehouse email:
    = current_user.email
  %div
    TalentLMS email:
    = current_user.talent_lms_email

%h2 Required Training Course Information
- @configs.sort_by(&:unique_name).each do |config|
  .well
    %h3= config.unique_name
    %p 
      Domain:
      = link_to config.domain, "https://#{config.domain}"
    .table-responsive
      %table.table.table-striped
        %thead
          %tr
            %th Course Name
            %th Course ID
            %th Course Completed
        %tbody
          - required_courses_for_config = (@courses & config.courses)
          - required_courses_for_config.each do |course|
            %tr
              %td= course.name
              %td= course.courseid
              %td= checkmark(course.completed_by?(current_user))

=render 'logout'